      "targeted_response_start": "",
      "beast_baseline": "i'm not really sure about the oil thing, it sounds kind of messy. honestly i'm pretty busy today and don't really want to go to a clinic if it's just a minor thing. are you sure it's not just like a pressure thing from the qtip? i feel like if i just sleep on it it'll pop back to normal in the morning.",
      "beast_suffix": "",
      "targeted_response_start_logprob": 0.0
    },
